name: Point Man
Lore: 'In a military situation, on a regional or galactic scale, commands sometimes get misinterpreted. A local commander giving orders is far more reliable.',
Text: 'Cancel Demotion, Restricted Deployment, Commence Recharging, Logistical Delay, They''re On Dantooine, Asteroid Sanctuary, Scramble, Order To Engage, No Disintegrations, Asteroids Do Not Concern Me, Report To Lord Vader or What Is Thy Bidding, My Master?',
